Do you want to stay here tonight?

106
00:04:30,033 --> 00:04:31,233
I mean

107
00:04:31,233 --> 00:04:32,867
I'll book you a room on the same floor as mine.

108
00:04:35,267 --> 00:04:35,933
Okay.

109
00:04:41,033 --> 00:04:41,867
This is it.

110
00:04:46,133 --> 00:04:47,400
Your room should be

111
