156
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,833
Wen Shuangjiang.

157
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,400
After all these years

158
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,300
I still

159
00:08:28,133 --> 00:08:28,933
