163
00:09:04,967 --> 00:09:05,467
Thank you.

164
00:09:05,467 --> 00:09:06,800
Enjoy your meal.

165
00:09:09,833 --> 00:09:11,200
So many takeaways.

166
00:09:11,367 --> 00:09:12,367
Are you hungry?

167
00:09:13,233 --> 00:09:14,000
I just

168
00:09:14,167 --> 00:09:14,833
