189
00:11:10,733 --> 00:11:11,500
No

190
00:11:12,433 --> 00:11:13,500
but just in case.

191
00:11:15,133 --> 00:11:16,267
Then I'll do the same later.

192
00:11:20,467 --> 00:11:21,967
I'm going back.

193
00:11:22,767 --> 00:11:24,500
I have to get up early tomorrow and go back.

194
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:25,467
I'll stop chatting.

195
00:11:25,567 --> 00:11:26,133
Good night.

196
00:11:32,267 --> 00:11:33,067
Sang Yan.

197
00:11:34,867 --> 00:11:35,500
What?

198
00:11:38,967 --> 00:11:39,767
Happy birthday.

199
00:11:44,633 --> 00:11:46,367
