218
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,367
Take a look at the screenshot I sent you.

219
00:12:45,833 --> 00:12:47,567
[Sang Yan]

220
00:12:47,567 --> 00:12:49,000
[Duan Jiaxu: Has your account been hacked?]

221
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,300
[Sang Yan: Sorry, my girlfriend asked me to post.]

222
00:12:52,467 --> 00:12:54,033
So he got the cake.

223
00:12:58,367 --> 00:13:01,267
[He wasn't hacked]

224
00:13:03,167 --> 00:13:04,233
[His girlfriend is me]

225
00:13:22,933 --> 00:13:23,433
Hello?

226
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:24,300
Hello?

227
00:13:24,333 --> 00:13:24,833
Dian.

228
00:13:24,867 --> 00:13:26,133
What's going on?

229
00:13:26,367 --> 00:13:28,200
Just like what I said.

230
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,467
It happened just now.

231
00:13:29,467 --> 00:13:31,000
