235
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:36,133
Did I?

236
00:13:36,133 --> 00:13:37,367
Yes.

237
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:39,967
You caused me to worry about you two.

238
00:13:39,967 --> 00:13:41,467
