239
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,433
Tell me.

240
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,033
How did it go so fast?

241
00:13:45,833 --> 00:13:47,967
Probably because I didn't control myself.

242
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:49,833
Gosh.

243
00:13:49,833 --> 00:13:51,167
Wen Yifan.

244
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:52,800
