257
00:14:40,733 --> 00:14:41,500
Because...

258
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,600
Sorry. I'm a little nervous.

259
00:14:46,133 --> 00:14:47,233
It's because

260
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:49,767
I don't want to be just friends with you.

261
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,033
I want to be your boyfriend

262
00:14:56,133 --> 00:14:56,633
