263
00:15:00,967 --> 00:15:02,133
Just confess like that?

264
00:15:04,967 --> 00:15:06,900
I'm next to your house right now.

265
00:15:08,033 --> 00:15:09,467
Anhe Bridge.

266
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:30,800
Xiang Lang?

267
00:15:32,567 --> 00:15:33,600
