268
00:15:33,733 --> 00:15:34,867
I just wanted to call you.

269
00:15:34,967 --> 00:15:36,000
I just got off the plane

270
00:15:36,267 --> 00:15:37,367
and wanted to surprise you.

271
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:39,000
We're on vacation at work

272
00:15:39,133 --> 00:15:40,233
so I wanted to come back and see you guys.

273
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:46,200
It's a bit of a shock.

274
00:15:46,233 --> 00:15:47,967
Why not a surprise but a shock?

275
00:15:48,433 --> 00:15:49,133
Actually

276
00:15:49,133 --> 00:15:51,233
it just so happens that a friend came to see me, too.

277
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:52,733
Meeting you this late?

278
00:15:56,167 --> 00:15:56,767
Dian?

279
00:15:57,167 --> 00:15:58,000
No.

280
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,467
It's a

281
00:15:59,767 --> 00:16:00,567
boy.

282
00:16:02,367 --> 00:16:03,400
Don't think too much.

283
00:16:03,633 --> 00:16:04,567
You know him, too.

284
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,467
I know him, too?

285
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:08,200
So can we

286
00:16:08,367 --> 00:16:09,133
go together?

287
00:16:11,267 --> 00:16:12,033
Maybe

288
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,367
OK.

289
00:16:21,267 --> 00:16:23,667
I've just learned some very shocking news.

290
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:26,200
I think you'll know it sooner or later.

291
00:16:26,633 --> 00:16:27,567
Dian

292
00:16:27,767 --> 00:16:30,233
is in love with Sang Yan.

293
00:16:35,633 --> 00:16:36,633
But that's good.

294
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:37,733
We should wish them well.

295
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,767
Are you sure you're okay?

296
00:16:41,633 --> 00:16:42,433
Of course.

297
00:16:43,433 --> 00:16:44,233
What about you?

298
00:16:44,867 --> 00:16:46,333
When can you care about yourself?

299
00:16:48,367 --> 00:16:49,067
I...

300
00:17:11,667 --> 00:17:12,300
I'm sorry

301
00:17:13,067 --> 00:17:14,100
to bother you

302
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:15,800
guys.

303
00:17:19,267 --> 00:17:21,367
You're the one who asked Qiao out so late.

304
00:17:21,433 --> 00:17:22,267
You're together?

305
00:17:24,267 --> 00:17:25,600
What a coincidence.

306
00:17:25,633 --> 00:17:27,933
He's here to see me too.

307
00:17:28,267 --> 00:17:28,867
Yes.

308
00:17:28,967 --> 00:17:30,300
I just came back from Hong Kong, China

309
00:17:30,433 --> 00:17:31,300
to meet my childhood friend.

310
00:17:32,767 --> 00:17:33,833
Actually

311
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:35,933
I have something important

312
00:17:35,933 --> 00:17:37,167
to talk to Qiao alone today

313
00:17:37,933 --> 00:17:38,967
but I didn't expect you to be here.

314
00:17:39,267 --> 00:17:40,200
But that's okay.

315
00:17:40,567 --> 00:17:41,733
As a man

316
00:17:42,033 --> 00:17:43,367
I don't need to hide anything.

317
00:17:44,100 --> 00:17:44,833
Zhong Siqiao.

318
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,267
I want you to be my...

319
00:17:47,267 --> 00:17:48,033
Wait.

320
00:17:48,267 --> 00:17:49,433
Don't be impulsive.

321
00:17:49,433 --> 00:17:50,667
Let's talk privately.

322
00:17:50,667 --> 00:17:52,233
What's so bad about this?

323
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:52,933
Qiao.

324
00:17:53,633 --> 00:17:54,633
Let him say.

325
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,000
But...

326
00:17:57,667 --> 00:17:58,767
Don't care about me.

327
00:17:59,033 --> 00:18:00,367
Grab your own happiness.

328
00:18:00,667 --> 00:18:02,600
- Su Haoan, I just feel... - Xiang Lang.

329
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:03,667
What do you mean?

330
00:18:04,267 --> 00:18:05,633
I think you may have misunderstood.

331
00:18:05,867 --> 00:18:07,167
Qiao and I

332
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,500
will always be best friends

333
00:18:08,933 --> 00:18:10,000
so Su Haoan

334
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:11,267
if you want to say something

335
00:18:12,167 --> 00:18:12,867
just say it.

336
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,067
Xiang Lang, don't you love Wen Yifan?

337
00:18:20,433 --> 00:18:21,800
I made it very clear just now.

338
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,800
So you've rejected Zhong Siqiao's confession?

339
00:18:26,867 --> 00:18:27,600
Yes.

340
00:18:27,767 --> 00:18:29,167
I confessed to Xiang Lang

341
00:18:29,167 --> 00:18:29,800
but he refused.

342
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:30,767
That was my wishful thinking

343
00:18:30,767 --> 00:18:31,467
okay?

344
00:18:31,467 --> 00:18:33,000
Both of you, stop it, okay?

345
00:18:33,167 --> 00:18:34,367
You still love him, don't you?

346
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,733
Of course not. How can that be?

347
00:18:35,733 --> 00:18:37,233
Then why don't you try to accept me?

348
00:18:37,233 --> 00:18:38,667
How can I try?

349
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:46,500
So it was my wishful thinking.

350
00:18:47,667 --> 00:18:48,400
I'm sorry

351
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:49,467
to bother you.

352
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,267
Su Haoan.

353
00:19:10,267 --> 00:19:10,933
Good morning.

354
00:19:11,867 --> 00:19:12,567
Good morning.

355
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:15,833
We're going to meet downstairs

356
00:19:15,867 --> 00:19:17,400
and probably have breakfast before going back.

357
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:18,600
Okay.

358
00:19:20,367 --> 00:19:21,233
Did you sleep well?

359
00:19:28,533 --> 00:19:29,033
Let's go.

360
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:32,633
Are you coming with us?

361
00:19:34,867 --> 00:19:35,500
Can't I?

362
00:20:18,733 --> 00:20:20,000
Hi. Check out.

363
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:20,600
Hi.

364
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:21,500
Me too.

365
00:20:21,767 --> 00:20:22,600
Okay. Just a moment.

366
00:20:24,567 --> 00:20:26,400
Ma'am. Confirm check-out.

367
00:20:28,067 --> 00:20:29,033
Morning, Ms. Qian.

368
00:20:29,033 --> 00:20:29,833
Done.

369
00:20:32,667 --> 00:20:33,467
It's you.

370
00:20:34,633 --> 00:20:35,600
Are you here for work

371
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,733
or pleasure?

372
00:20:36,833 --> 00:20:37,433
I'm here to see her.

373
00:20:39,933 --> 00:20:41,100
Let's go check out.

374
00:20:41,967 --> 00:20:42,567
Okay.

375
00:20:43,067 --> 00:20:44,600
Check out for me. I need to confirm something.

376
00:20:48,633 --> 00:20:49,600
Sang Yan.

377
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:52,033
I know you want to see Yifan

378
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,800
but I'm afraid it's not right for you

379
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,967
to follow her even when she's traveling.

380
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,633
Yifan has a good personality

381
00:20:59,367 --> 00:21:01,000
so she won't get mad at you

382
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,767
but you have to think

383
00:21:02,767 --> 00:21:03,800
about her feelings a bit.

384
00:21:15,267 --> 00:21:16,467
You're courting her like this.

385
00:21:17,233 --> 00:21:18,400
No wonder it doesn't work.

386
00:21:19,233 --> 00:21:20,767
It just puts pressure on her.

387
00:21:28,067 --> 00:21:29,400
We're long past that stage.

388
00:21:30,433 --> 00:21:31,800
Have you got everything?

389
00:21:32,033 --> 00:21:33,367
We are now having

390
00:21:33,733 --> 00:21:37,000
mutual feelings.

391
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:39,800
Ever heard

392
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:40,500
that phrase?

393
00:21:45,233 --> 00:21:46,033
Have you?

394
00:21:47,167 --> 00:21:47,967
Who said that?

395
00:21:49,167 --> 00:21:50,000
Me.

396
00:21:50,167 --> 00:21:51,033
I'm glad you admit it.

397
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:54,800
Ms. Qian.

398
00:21:55,233 --> 00:21:56,600
Let me drive. Take a break.

399
00:21:57,267 --> 00:21:58,000
It's okay.

400
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,100
I've been up so late these days

401
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:00,600
that my bones almost fell apart.

402
00:22:00,633 --> 00:22:01,367
Thank you.

403
00:22:01,367 --> 00:22:02,067
You're welcome.

404
00:22:02,467 --> 00:22:03,267
I'm sorry.

405
00:22:03,367 --> 00:22:04,200
I'm supposed to drive

406
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,367
but I don't have a license.

407
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,067
Let me help you.

408
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:09,200
Thank you.

409
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:10,967
I'll drive.

410
00:22:11,767 --> 00:22:12,767
Didn't you take a cab?

411
00:22:15,933 --> 00:22:16,633
Give me directions.

412
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,033
But we have to get to the TV station first.

413
00:22:22,567 --> 00:22:23,600
All right. Get in the car.

414
00:22:36,833 --> 00:22:37,633
Qiao.

415
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,000
Sorry to keep you waiting.

416
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,067
Dian.

417
00:22:42,067 --> 00:22:42,867
Xiang Lang.

418
00:22:43,467 --> 00:22:44,467
When did you come back?

419
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:45,833
Not long ago.

420
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:53,233
What happened to you?

421
00:22:54,833 --> 00:22:56,367
I didn't sleep well last night.

422
00:22:57,867 --> 00:22:59,500
Is it because of me?

423
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:02,267
You don't have to keep your voice down.

424
00:23:02,267 --> 00:23:03,867
I've already accidentally let him know.

425
00:23:05,267 --> 00:23:06,067
Besides

426
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:07,400
I'm very happy

427
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:08,600
that you're in love with Sang Yan.

428
00:23:08,767 --> 00:23:09,667
So what happened to you?

429
00:23:12,633 --> 00:23:13,467
Yesterday

430
00:23:13,933 --> 00:23:14,867
I happened to bump into Su Haoan

431
00:23:14,867 --> 00:23:16,567
confessing his love to Qiao

432
00:23:16,733 --> 00:23:17,433
but

433
00:23:17,433 --> 00:23:19,033
he was ruthlessly rejected by Qiao.

434
00:23:19,833 --> 00:23:21,167
Su Haoan was almost crashed.

435
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:24,367
Really?

436
00:23:24,367 --> 00:23:25,233
Su Haoan?

437
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,833
You think it's unbelievable too, don't you?

438
00:23:28,367 --> 00:23:29,367
He loves you?

439
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:31,267
Do you love him?

440
00:23:33,667 --> 00:23:34,567
I don't know

441
00:23:35,433 --> 00:23:37,367
but when I don't see him

442
00:23:37,367 --> 00:23:37,933
I'll wonder

443
00:23:37,933 --> 00:23:39,600
why I can't hear from him at all.

444
00:23:40,567 --> 00:23:42,200
And yet, as soon as we met...

445
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:43,267
He confessed to her.

446
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:45,667
Anyway, when I met him

447
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,833
all sorts of strange things happened.

448
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:49,000
So maybe

449
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,967
it's a kind of fate.

450
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:53,800
No way.

451
00:23:53,867 --> 00:23:54,833
We're not even the same species

452
00:23:54,833 --> 00:23:55,833
on Earth.

453
00:23:57,567 --> 00:23:59,233
You're always the professional

454
00:23:59,233 --> 00:24:00,433
when guiding me in my relationships.

455
00:24:00,933 --> 00:24:02,000
How is this the same?

456
00:24:02,033 --> 00:24:02,767
That's enough.

457
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:05,367
Su Haoan seems a little mindless

458
00:24:05,467 --> 00:24:07,033
[Su Haoan requests to be your friend]
but I think

459
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:09,667
[I'm Su Haoan. Before you go

460
00:24:09,933 --> 00:24:11,167
[can we talk?]
You're different from him.

461
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,767
You seem to have a big heart

462
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:15,167
but have a lot of worries.

463
00:24:15,467 --> 00:24:16,733
Don't you complement each other?

464
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:19,200
Don't you want to give it a try?

465
00:24:20,833 --> 00:24:21,967
Forget it. I won't.

466
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:22,733
Let's eat.

467
00:24:23,667 --> 00:24:24,367
Okay.

468
00:24:27,133 --> 00:24:30,033
[Uptown Flower City]

469
00:24:30,033 --> 00:24:31,200
Home at last.

470
00:24:57,567 --> 00:24:59,000
Aren't you forgetting something?

471
00:25:06,500 --> 00:25:07,300
Just give me a second.

472
00:25:51,233 --> 00:25:51,967
A coat?

473
00:26:15,867 --> 00:26:17,800
Why this color?

474
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:19,467
Because I haven't seen you

475
00:26:19,467 --> 00:26:20,933
wear this color.

476
00:26:21,033 --> 00:26:22,467
I feel it suits you.

477
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,800
Your hat.

478
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:36,400
You don't like it?

479
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:39,167
Then I'll give you another present.

480
00:26:40,767 --> 00:26:41,933
Who says I don't like it?

481
00:26:44,033 --> 00:26:45,567
I've received quite a few gifts this year.

482
00:26:46,667 --> 00:26:48,467
In terms of satisfaction

483
00:26:51,500 --> 00:26:52,433
this one can be ranked second.

484
00:26:53,833 --> 00:26:55,100
And what's number one?

485
00:26:57,467 --> 00:26:58,400
The one I got yesterday.

486
00:26:58,800 --> 00:26:59,433
What's that?

487
00:26:59,667 --> 00:27:00,467
What do you think?

488
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:04,267
Let me guess.

489
00:27:13,733 --> 00:27:14,400
Thank you.

490
00:27:22,633 --> 00:27:23,600
As long as you like it.

491
00:27:28,767 --> 00:27:30,033
Stop thinking.

492
00:27:31,667 --> 00:27:32,500
You're number one.

493
00:27:40,367 --> 00:27:41,033
What's wrong?

494
00:27:43,733 --> 00:27:44,400
Did you put the medicine on?

495
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:47,600
It scabbed over.

496
00:27:57,033 --> 00:27:58,467
It's really not that bad.

497
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,067
This thing

498
00:28:00,067 --> 00:28:01,167
will heal naturally.

499
00:28:04,067 --> 00:28:05,633
The atmosphere's a little gritty

500
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:06,767
so I've got to think of a way

501
00:28:06,767 --> 00:28:08,200
to keep him from being serious.

502
00:28:08,533 --> 00:28:11,700
♪Meeting you made me start acting foolish♪

503
00:28:12,333 --> 00:28:15,900
♪My heart races, and even my breath pauses♪

504
00:28:16,333 --> 00:28:17,267
♪I can't...♪

505
00:28:18,267 --> 00:28:18,967
It hurts.

506
00:28:22,767 --> 00:28:23,633
Are you blackmailing me?

507
00:28:23,767 --> 00:28:24,633
Why so far away from me?

508
00:28:31,833 --> 00:28:32,433
Come over a little.

509
00:28:37,233 --> 00:28:38,600
Don't take liberties with me by that.

510
00:28:41,667 --> 00:28:42,667
I'll be careful.

511
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:48,000
Can you control your force?

512
00:28:50,267 --> 00:28:52,000
Do journalists have to learn acting?

513
00:28:56,100 --> 00:28:57,100
Actually, I didn't care much

514
00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:58,067
about the wound after it scabbed over.

515
00:28:58,067 --> 00:28:59,633
I thought it was almost healed.

516
00:28:59,833 --> 00:29:02,300
So you guys always get hurt on the job?

517
00:29:02,433 --> 00:29:06,167
♪Like a long passed mysterious love spell♪

518
00:29:06,300 --> 00:29:09,933
♪Like a noisy afternoon suddenly turning quiet♪

519
00:29:11,367 --> 00:29:12,267
Now it doesn't hurt?

520
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,967
All right. Go get some rest.

521
00:29:28,467 --> 00:29:30,233
Come back to me tomorrow after your bath.

522
00:29:38,667 --> 00:29:40,100
Isn't this too soon?

523
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:46,567
What are you thinking about?

524
00:29:47,167 --> 00:29:48,200
I'm going to put medicine on you.

525
00:30:20,967 --> 00:30:22,367
Yifan, let's go.

526
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:33,200
Yifan.

527
00:30:35,433 --> 00:30:36,200
Fu Zhuang, excuse me.

528
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:37,567
Let me take her a few minutes.

529
00:30:37,733 --> 00:30:38,833
Yifan, I'll wait for you in the car.

530
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,033
OK.

531
00:30:41,267 --> 00:30:42,033
What's wrong?

532
00:30:46,433 --> 00:30:47,767
I don't understand

533
00:30:47,933 --> 00:30:48,733
why you're in love

534
00:30:48,733 --> 00:30:50,300
with Sang Yan.

535
00:30:50,667 --> 00:30:52,600
I really can't find anything good about him.

536
00:30:52,767 --> 00:30:53,567
Why do you

537
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,467
have to compromise yourself?

538
00:30:56,767 --> 00:30:57,667
I didn't.

539
00:30:59,433 --> 00:31:00,667
Has he ever tried to confess to you?

540
00:31:09,667 --> 00:31:10,433
He cares about me like

541
00:31:10,433 --> 00:31:11,833
he's confessing to me every day.

542
00:31:11,833 --> 00:31:13,100
Can he be like that?

543
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:16,267
I don't care.

544
00:31:16,933 --> 00:31:17,633
If he dares

545
00:31:17,867 --> 00:31:19,200
to break your heart

546
00:31:19,800 --> 00:31:21,400
I can get back at him hard for you.

547
00:31:23,767 --> 00:31:24,967
Okay. Thanks.

548
00:31:29,767 --> 00:31:31,233
Actually, I've been in love with him

549
00:31:31,233 --> 00:31:32,367
since high school.

550
00:31:32,867 --> 00:31:34,433
I just never admitted it.

551
00:31:39,267 --> 00:31:41,000
I feel happy to be in love

552
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,267
with him now.

553
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,033
OK.

554
00:31:46,733 --> 00:31:47,733
You'll meet someone

555
00:31:47,733 --> 00:31:49,233
who cherishes you in the future.

556
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,200
I'm going to work.

557
00:32:00,967 --> 00:32:01,667
Here's the dish.

558
00:32:03,633 --> 00:32:04,400
Main course.

559
00:32:04,733 --> 00:32:05,933
Fish in muddy water.

560
00:32:06,567 --> 00:32:07,400
What are you doing?

561
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:08,867
Serving.

562
00:32:08,867 --> 00:32:10,133
[Eating tofu jelly]

563
00:32:11,767 --> 00:32:12,567
Taste it.

564
00:32:12,633 --> 00:32:14,233
What's the plan for after dinner?

565
00:32:15,067 --> 00:32:16,700
[Nothing yet]

566
00:32:17,767 --> 00:32:18,933
Then come to Overtime.

567
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:23,333
[Aren't you partying with them?]

568
00:32:24,833 --> 00:32:26,400
It's so boring. Be with me.

569
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:32,467
We'll be right there.

570
00:32:32,933 --> 00:32:33,633
Where are we going?

571
00:32:34,300 --> 00:32:35,067
To Overtime.

572
00:32:35,067 --> 00:32:35,833
Let's go.

573
00:32:44,633 --> 00:32:46,933
Do they know you're in love with Sang Yan?

574
00:32:47,667 --> 00:32:49,000
Probably not.

575
00:32:49,067 --> 00:32:50,000
I didn't ask.

576
00:32:50,467 --> 00:32:51,733
Since you're already in love

577
00:32:51,733 --> 00:32:53,000
ask if you want to.

578
00:32:53,733 --> 00:32:54,300
Wait.

579
00:32:54,733 --> 00:32:55,800
Feel my heartbeat.

580
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:56,500
Why is it racing?

581
00:32:56,500 --> 00:32:57,433
I'm so nervous.

582
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:58,633
Why are you nervous?

583
00:32:59,267 --> 00:32:59,967
Please.

584
00:32:59,967 --> 00:33:00,867
This will be the first time

585
00:33:00,867 --> 00:33:03,000
Sang Yan appeared in front of me

586
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:03,967
as my best friend's boyfriend.

587
00:33:03,967 --> 00:33:05,367
I don't even know how to face him.

588
00:33:05,933 --> 00:33:06,733
Let me see where he is.

589
00:33:12,100 --> 00:33:13,800
Just do the same as before.

590
00:33:15,233 --> 00:33:15,933
OK.

591
00:33:18,967 --> 00:33:19,767
Indeed

592
00:33:20,233 --> 00:33:22,100
I'm also a bit overwhelmed by the change

593
00:33:22,633 --> 00:33:24,367
in our relationship after so many years.

594
00:33:32,067 --> 00:33:33,467
Taste what I just cooked today.

595
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,767
Taste the fish in muddy water.

596
00:33:40,300 --> 00:33:41,500
- There you are. - Hello.

597
00:33:41,533 --> 00:33:42,200
- There you are. - Hello.

598
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,267
- Welcome. - Hello.

599
00:33:43,267 --> 00:33:44,367
- Sit down. - Come on.

600
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,400
Come on.

601
00:33:45,800 --> 00:33:46,500
- Come on, Yifan. - Thank you.

602
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:47,133
Sit next to me.

603
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,233
Here. Use this.

604
00:33:49,667 --> 00:33:50,767
Thank you.

605
00:33:53,933 --> 00:33:55,000
What are you doing?

606
00:33:55,933 --> 00:33:57,767
- What do you mean? - Thanks.

607
00:33:58,267 --> 00:33:59,967
Don't you have a girlfriend?

608
00:33:59,967 --> 00:34:00,933
Why do you invite other girls

609
00:34:00,933 --> 00:34:01,833
to sit next to you?

610
00:34:02,033 --> 00:34:02,767
Don't ask.

611
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:09,500
Looks like he hasn't told them yet.

612
00:34:13,467 --> 00:34:14,233
Why are you looking at me?

613
00:34:14,233 --> 00:34:15,967
It's the first time I've seen you in khaki.

614
00:34:16,067 --> 00:34:17,000
No wonder

615
00:34:17,167 --> 00:34:18,567
l felt something strange about Yan today.

616
00:34:18,567 --> 00:34:20,433
It's so obvious, but you're just now realizing it?

617
00:34:20,567 --> 00:34:21,867
What's the point of wearing this?

618
00:34:22,033 --> 00:34:23,000
It's so flirty.

619
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,367
Are you the hero of a movie?

620
00:34:24,467 --> 00:34:25,267
Right, Yifan?

621
00:34:26,033 --> 00:34:26,700
Right?

622
00:34:27,833 --> 00:34:28,800
Maybe.

623
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,233
I think it's quite manly.

624
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:32,933
You don't have an aesthetic.

625
00:34:33,433 --> 00:34:35,367
My girlfriend bought it for me.

626
00:34:35,433 --> 00:34:36,433
She likes this color.

627
00:34:37,333 --> 00:34:37,933
Girlfriend?

628
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:39,833
Oh, my God.

629
00:34:40,500 --> 00:34:42,833
You're moving too fast with your girlfriend.

630
00:34:42,967 --> 00:34:44,033
How long have you been in love?

631
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,833
You called her girlfriend.

632
00:34:45,833 --> 00:34:46,667
Wine.

633
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:48,567
- Thank you. - Looking good.

634
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:49,267
Thank you.

635
00:34:50,033 --> 00:34:50,867
Come on. Taste it.

636
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,500
She doesn't drink.

637
00:34:53,067 --> 00:34:53,700
Right?

638
00:34:54,233 --> 00:34:54,867
Sang Yan.

639
00:34:55,167 --> 00:34:56,633
We've been sitting here all afternoon

640
00:34:56,633 --> 00:34:58,000
and you haven't had a drink

641
00:34:58,500 --> 00:34:59,933
but now you're taking Yifan's.

642
00:35:00,033 --> 00:35:00,800
I don't drink either.

643
00:35:01,167 --> 00:35:01,767
I'm going to drive.

644
00:35:01,867 --> 00:35:03,367
Sang Yan, you're so weird

645
00:35:03,767 --> 00:35:04,567
but

646
00:35:04,567 --> 00:35:05,667
I have to kindly remind you

647
00:35:05,667 --> 00:35:07,400
who's been single since birth

648
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:08,567
not to be like me.

649
00:35:08,567 --> 00:35:09,967
Don't worry. I won't.

650
00:35:10,233 --> 00:35:11,033
Yan.

651
00:35:11,767 --> 00:35:13,500
I'd also like to remind you

652
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:15,567
to restrain yourself

653
00:35:16,767 --> 00:35:17,800
so you won't scare away

654
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,333
the only woman in the world

655
00:35:19,333 --> 00:35:21,367
who can put up with your bad temper.

656
00:35:22,033 --> 00:35:23,267
It's not sure if he has a girlfriend or not.

657
00:35:24,467 --> 00:35:25,167
OK.

658
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:27,467
I won't be like you either.

659
00:35:27,633 --> 00:35:29,067
Can I be a backup like you or...

660
00:35:30,667 --> 00:35:32,000
She only likes people like me.

661
00:35:33,033 --> 00:35:34,067
So when are you gonna

662
00:35:34,067 --> 00:35:35,467
bring your girlfriend over

663
00:35:35,667 --> 00:35:37,233
and show us?

664
00:35:37,433 --> 00:35:38,000
Right?

665
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,100
How many days has it been?

666
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:40,100
Or

667
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:41,100
are you so unsure

668
00:35:41,100 --> 00:35:42,333
that you're afraid your girlfriend will fall in love with me

669
00:35:42,433 --> 00:35:43,167
when she gets here?

670
00:35:45,033 --> 00:35:45,767
Stop bragging.

671
00:35:45,767 --> 00:35:46,633
It's a pipe dream.

672
00:35:47,433 --> 00:35:48,067
See you later.

673
00:35:48,067 --> 00:35:48,867
Look. He's gone again.

674
00:35:49,100 --> 00:35:50,300
- Nonsense. - Bye-bye.

675
00:35:50,333 --> 00:35:51,267
Bye.

676
00:35:53,233 --> 00:35:54,100
Come on, Yifan.

677
00:35:57,367 --> 00:35:57,967
Are you leaving, too?

678
00:35:57,967 --> 00:35:58,500
You're going, too?

679
00:35:58,500 --> 00:35:59,400
With him?

680
00:35:59,667 --> 00:36:00,633
No. Come back. Sit down.

681
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:01,567
Don't go.

682
00:36:01,567 --> 00:36:03,033
Sang Yan.

683
00:36:03,100 --> 00:36:04,767
You have a girlfriend

684
00:36:04,767 --> 00:36:06,100
but why do you still hang out

685
00:36:06,267 --> 00:36:07,467
with your roommate every day?

686
00:36:07,467 --> 00:36:08,700
What's the matter with you?

687
00:36:09,067 --> 00:36:11,400
Is your girlfriend okay with this?

688
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:12,333
It's inappropriate.

689
00:36:12,333 --> 00:36:13,467
Think about it.

690
00:36:14,267 --> 00:36:16,033
Two idiots.

691
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:17,867
See you later.

692
00:36:17,867 --> 00:36:18,867
- Qiao. - Just go. Don't worry about me.

693
00:36:18,867 --> 00:36:19,867
Qiao, don't go.

694
00:36:19,867 --> 00:36:20,433
I won't.

695
00:36:20,433 --> 00:36:21,800
- Stay here. - Don't get too close.

696
00:36:22,267 --> 00:36:22,800
Yeah.

697
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:23,433
Come on. Let's drink.

698
00:36:23,433 --> 00:36:23,967
Come on.

699
00:36:23,967 --> 00:36:24,867
- Come on. - Try my new dish.

700
00:36:24,867 --> 00:36:25,400
OK.

701
00:36:25,500 --> 00:36:26,567
Come on.

702
00:36:27,067 --> 00:36:28,400
Didn't you tell them

703
00:36:28,567 --> 00:36:29,633
your girlfriend was me?

704
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:33,000
I didn't think they'd be able to tell.

705
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:36,467
I'd better tell them in a formal setting.

706
00:36:38,267 --> 00:36:38,967
What?

707
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:39,767
You can't wait?

708
00:36:40,267 --> 00:36:41,967
I'm just curious.

709
00:36:45,067 --> 00:36:46,400
Is this coat really nice?

710
00:36:46,633 --> 00:36:47,267
Of course.

711
00:36:48,067 --> 00:36:48,867
Both the shape

712
00:36:49,367 --> 00:36:50,167
and the fabric.

713
00:36:50,933 --> 00:36:51,767
And it's very warm, too.

714
00:36:51,933 --> 00:36:52,767
I'm even sweating.

715
00:36:55,200 --> 00:36:55,933
I was going to say

716
00:36:55,933 --> 00:36:57,233
that this color

717
00:36:57,367 --> 00:36:59,200
might make you look a little softer

718
00:37:00,267 --> 00:37:01,200
but I didn't expect...

719
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,100
Didn't expect what?

720
00:37:02,967 --> 00:37:04,333
I didn't expect it

721
00:37:04,967 --> 00:37:06,267
to be as cocky as you are.

722
00:37:08,633 --> 00:37:09,200
What?

723
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:10,867
Shocked by how handsome your boyfriend is?

724
00:37:13,100 --> 00:37:14,267
Whatever you say.

725
00:37:15,667 --> 00:37:16,600
Have dinner with me.

726
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:17,967
Didn't you eat just now?

727
00:37:18,467 --> 00:37:19,667
No. I was waiting for you.

728
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,200
Have you eaten?

729
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:26,767
A little.

730
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:30,800
Didn't I just show you a picture?

731
00:37:48,167 --> 00:37:49,000
What do you mean?

732
00:37:49,700 --> 00:37:50,600
Are you settling a score with me

733
00:37:51,433 --> 00:37:52,667
or to show your hand to your rival?

734
00:37:53,767 --> 00:37:54,567
Sit down and talk.

735
00:38:04,367 --> 00:38:05,067
Have some water.

736
00:38:08,367 --> 00:38:09,333
I know you're busy

737
00:38:09,567 --> 00:38:10,367
so I'm sorry

738
00:38:11,967 --> 00:38:14,433
but I really don't know who to talk to.

739
00:38:14,933 --> 00:38:16,367
I had a really hard time before.

740
00:38:16,933 --> 00:38:18,233
I've never felt this way before.

741
00:38:19,433 --> 00:38:21,033
I just want to know more about her.

742
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:22,700
Of course, I wanted to ask Wen Yifan at first

743
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,433
but I felt

744
00:38:25,633 --> 00:38:26,700
that Qiao would be angry

745
00:38:27,467 --> 00:38:28,433
if she knew

746
00:38:28,633 --> 00:38:29,567
so after thinking it over

747
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:32,767
I asked you to come here.

748
00:38:36,067 --> 00:38:36,933
Actually

749
00:38:39,067 --> 00:38:40,067
Qiao wasn't as happy

750
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,667
as she seemed

751
00:38:42,167 --> 00:38:43,333
but she always played along

752
00:38:43,667 --> 00:38:45,000
without saying anything.

753
00:38:46,033 --> 00:38:48,167
When she was a sophomore in high school

754
00:38:50,233 --> 00:38:52,067
Dian moved to Beiyu.

755
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:53,267
Actually, she was never happy

756
00:38:53,267 --> 00:38:54,333
during that time.

757
00:38:54,867 --> 00:38:56,033
When I came back to see her

758
00:38:56,233 --> 00:38:57,800
during my first winter break

759
00:38:58,067 --> 00:38:59,200
she didn't accept that

760
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,400
right away.

761
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,633
It was very unlike her before.

762
00:39:03,567 --> 00:39:04,167
I expected you

763
00:39:04,167 --> 00:39:05,400
to extort a big meal from me

764
00:39:05,667 --> 00:39:06,867
but I didn't expect you to treat me to a cake.

765
00:39:07,367 --> 00:39:08,233
Why don't you eat it?

766
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,400
I suddenly feel

767
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,567
that the three of us have become so distant.

768
00:39:14,033 --> 00:39:15,433
Nanwu Trio?

769
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:16,933
No one even cares about that.

770
00:39:19,167 --> 00:39:19,867
What's wrong with you?

771
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:22,600
Did something happen to you recently?

772
00:39:24,033 --> 00:39:25,933
Do things have to happen to me to make me miss you?

773
00:39:26,167 --> 00:39:26,967
Do friends have to care about each other

774
00:39:26,967 --> 00:39:29,367
when something happens to them?

775
00:39:32,967 --> 00:39:35,500
We've all been a little busy lately.

776
00:39:37,167 --> 00:39:37,867
Yes.

777
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:40,033
You're all busy.

778
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:42,433
You don't have to make time

779
00:39:42,433 --> 00:39:43,667
to see me during the short time

780
00:39:43,667 --> 00:39:45,100
you're here.

781
00:39:53,333 --> 00:39:54,000
Qiao.

782
00:39:55,367 --> 00:39:56,167
I'm sorry.

783
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:59,067
Do you know why I bought the cake?

784
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:01,800
Because you're going back soon.

785
00:40:01,800 --> 00:40:03,567
Your birthday is on March 14th.

786
00:40:03,567 --> 00:40:05,467
I was worried no one would celebrate your birthday there

787
00:40:05,467 --> 00:40:06,667
so I bought it.

788
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:10,267
I remember your and Dian's birthday every year

789
00:40:10,267 --> 00:40:11,500
but what about you guys? Do you remember mine?

790
00:40:16,467 --> 00:40:17,433
She always remembers

791
00:40:17,433 --> 00:40:19,100
what everyone likes

792
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:21,667
and our birthdays.

793
00:40:23,767 --> 00:40:24,867
It's like we're all used

794
00:40:25,200 --> 00:40:26,600
to her being there.

795
00:40:28,867 --> 00:40:30,067
She's often not the one

796
00:40:30,067 --> 00:40:31,333
at the center

797
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,433
but

798
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:33,767
the one at the center

799
00:40:34,467 --> 00:40:35,400
sure needs her.

800
00:40:42,233 --> 00:40:43,867
Can you

801
00:40:44,100 --> 00:40:45,100
tell me more?

802
00:40:49,633 --> 00:40:50,833
Would you like some?

803
00:40:51,033 --> 00:40:51,867
Talk while eating.

804
00:40:56,633 --> 00:40:57,767
I just feel like I don't know

805
00:40:59,033 --> 00:41:00,100
anything about her

806
00:41:00,367 --> 00:41:01,033
so I'd like to learn more

807
00:41:01,767 --> 00:41:03,000
about her.

808
00:41:06,467 --> 00:41:07,667
I thought of one more thing.

809
00:41:09,933 --> 00:41:11,267
Actually, during that time

810
00:41:11,433 --> 00:41:13,600
it wasn't all because of Dian that she was unhappy.

811
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:16,000
At that time

812
00:41:16,833 --> 00:41:17,867
her mom and dad were about to be divorced.

813
00:41:24,833 --> 00:41:26,833
Which flavor of dumpling would you like?

814
00:41:29,233 --> 00:41:31,233
Or do you want to order something else?

815
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:33,233
Take your pick.

816
00:41:33,233 --> 00:41:34,767
I owe you a meal anyway.

817
00:41:36,233 --> 00:41:36,767
But

818
00:41:37,033 --> 00:41:37,800
this one doesn't count.

819
00:41:41,200 --> 00:41:41,967
You decide.

820
00:41:42,033 --> 00:41:43,233
What do you want to eat?

821
00:41:43,933 --> 00:41:45,633
Don't you have a lot of taboos?

822
00:41:48,433 --> 00:41:49,567
Not anymore.

823
00:41:51,167 --> 00:41:52,067
What are you looking at?

824
00:41:54,267 --> 00:41:55,767
That lamp is pretty.

825
00:41:57,167 --> 00:41:57,833
Now eat.

826
00:42:02,267 --> 00:42:03,367
Do you like it?

827
00:42:04,433 --> 00:42:05,500
I ordered something

828
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:06,600
with strong flavors.

829
00:42:09,567 --> 00:42:10,833
Do you like it?

830
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:12,867
Don't you like mild food?

831
00:42:14,333 --> 00:42:17,067
I tried to imagine what you like.

832
00:42:23,667 --> 00:42:25,367
I do like dumplings quite a bit.

833
00:42:30,967 --> 00:42:31,667
What

834
00:42:31,667 --> 00:42:32,333
are you looking at?

835
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:34,933
The ferris wheel.

836
00:42:38,067 --> 00:42:39,033
Let's eat

837
00:42:39,467 --> 00:42:40,167
quickly then.

838
00:42:40,667 --> 00:42:41,433
When we're done

839
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:42,333
let's go there.

840
00:42:45,833 --> 00:42:48,967
[Episode 19]

841
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:51,933
[Bai Jiang doesn't mean I'm a loser but that I only lost to you, Wen Shuangjiang]

842
00:43:04,367 --> 00:43:06,100
[The story is not over yet...]

843
00:43:06,100 --> 00:43:07,400
Hello, sir. The things you want.

844
00:43:07,833 --> 00:43:08,433
Thank you.

845
00:43:26,367 --> 00:43:27,200
What are you looking at?

846
00:43:27,600 --> 00:43:28,233
This is mine.

847
00:43:52,033 --> 00:43:54,733
[Sang Yan, Happy Birthday!]

848
00:44:04,467 --> 00:44:05,767
♪Even the strongest heart♪

849
00:44:05,933 --> 00:44:07,633
♪Can waver♪

850
00:44:07,867 --> 00:44:11,067
♪And doubt its fire♪

851
00:44:11,300 --> 00:44:12,933
♪But you never lost faith in me♪

852
00:44:12,933 --> 00:44:14,633
♪In every battle, every dream I chased♪

853
00:44:14,833 --> 00:44:17,500
♪There is meaning in every step I made♪

854
00:44:18,333 --> 00:44:24,300
♪Through the storm, through the endless night♪

855
00:44:24,667 --> 00:44:26,300
♪You were there, shining like a light♪

856
00:44:26,300 --> 00:44:27,967
♪Warm and bright♪

857
00:44:28,133 --> 00:44:31,867
♪Standing right by my side♪

858
00:44:32,300 --> 00:44:38,433
♪It was you, striding toward me through the storm♪

859
00:44:38,767 --> 00:44:45,700
♪It was you, always cheering me on♪

860
00:44:45,867 --> 00:44:48,867
♪The road is rough♪

861
00:44:49,167 --> 00:44:53,300
♪The rain won't stop♪

862
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:57,467
♪But with you here♪

863
00:44:57,733 --> 00:45:03,767
♪I fear no dark♪

864
00:45:07,033 --> 00:45:10,633
♪Every thought, every memory is filled with you♪

865
00:45:10,933 --> 00:45:14,433
♪Marking our youth with every step we took♪

866
00:45:14,700 --> 00:45:16,567
♪When the downpour falls from the sky♪

867
00:45:16,567 --> 00:45:20,233
♪You're the one holding out an umbrella for me♪

868
00:45:20,567 --> 00:45:24,133
♪When the white dove brings the news♪

869
00:45:24,500 --> 00:45:27,933
♪You're the first I want to tell♪

870
00:45:28,333 --> 00:45:36,967
♪I won't give up. I'll stay right here with you♪

871
00:45:41,567 --> 00:45:47,767
♪It was you, striding toward me through the storm♪

872
00:45:48,633 --> 00:45:55,067
♪It was you, always cheering me on♪

873
00:45:55,067 --> 00:45:58,233
♪The road is rough♪

874
00:45:58,700 --> 00:46:02,667
♪The rain won't stop♪

875
00:46:02,867 --> 00:46:05,500
♪But with you here♪

876
00:46:05,700 --> 00:46:09,533
♪I will never give up♪

877
00:46:09,833 --> 00:46:15,900
♪You are my courage, my hope for the sky beyond♪

878
00:46:16,433 --> 00:46:22,267
♪You are my light, shining through every night♪

879
00:46:22,833 --> 00:46:25,667
♪Even if I have to walk alone someday♪

880
00:46:26,100 --> 00:46:28,933
♪I'll never truly be on my own♪

881
00:46:29,967 --> 00:46:34,500
♪'Cause knowing you're here♪

882
00:46:34,933 --> 00:46:41,533
♪I can brave the dark ahead♪

883
00:46:43,333 --> 00:46:44,600
[Huge thanks to everyone involved and to all the fans of The First Frost!]

884
00:46:44,600 --> 00:46:45,733
[Treat yourself well, and the world will hold more love for you!]
